similarly

    [Documentation]  Get all the available sensors for the required component.
    ...  Returns a list of available sensors.
    [Arguments]  ${sensor_component}
Please add example of IPMI sensor command output
Add an example for sensor get command

One space after #. Also align the text like below
    # Locating sensor record...
    # Sensor ID              : dcm0_cpu0 (0x41)
    # Entity ID              : 3.1
    # Sensor Type (Discrete) : Processor

    ${line}=  Get Lines Containing String  ${get_resp}  Sensor ID
    ${sensor_id}=  Set Variable  ${line[-5:-1]}
why are we skipping the sensors, if an sensor is not having reading value.

Now making use of "Presence detected" in sdr elist command to get the available sensors instead of reading value.
